    <description>The QBZ-95 (Chinese: 97式自动步枪; pinyin: 95 Shì Zìdòng Bùqiāng; literally: 'Type 95 Automatic Rifle') is a bullpup-style assault rifle designed and manufactured by Norinco for the People's Liberation Army, the armed forces of the People's Republic of China, People's Armed Police (para-military police), and other Chinese law enforcement agencies.
	
